{"tid":292963,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"相信所有人都係自己既分身","createTime":"2017-06-21T19:01:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-22T15:40:37.000Z","uid":76098,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"164e2349fdc3cd3af6f29c05381861ca11eb9003","tid":292963,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T19:01:05.000Z","msg":"姐係你，其實係某個階段，或者某個轉世既我 <br />\n唔係痴左線，而係如果將呢個諗法當係一種信仰，人會唔會變得識自省，而且向善?"},{"pid":"9b348daf308ca7bad2d16a8378875abfb68c910d","tid":292963,"uid":81782,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T19:10:04.000Z","msg":"我以前都有咁諗過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f72cba61313599d6e37288e210a6b3d744fdef73","tid":292963,"uid":54177,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T19:24:29.000Z","msg":"我個版本係轉生<br />\n<br />\n其實我生活左幾百年<br />\n上幾世人都好成功帶動社會進步<br />\n發夢記得之前我個幾世人係聰明到預知/測到各種事情, 所以好易成功<br />\n<br />\n今世d基因差左小小, 遲發育<br />\n結果做緊廢青<br />\n我諗緊依個我係咪我黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然20歲d感覺開始返返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a83c5c7b6fb4d34dca2f41aa55f313ebc7ffa1c3","tid":292963,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T02:03:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"902cbacfbc6dbc500cbd6d7dbd91fec5f76cb8ff","tid":292963,"uid":8386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T04:03:27.000Z","msg":"唔太明樓主既意思,<br />\n點解當我係你某一世既轉世或者某階段時,<br />\n我會有可能自省, 或者會向善?<br />\n動機係咩? 理由係咩?"},{"pid":"4bf8b45dc3c047303b29425a6b29ac523e23e816","tid":292963,"uid":86893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T04:18:42.000Z","msg":"牙籤仔變巨龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecd8c4dcc869dffca8cd330ae99eeb20c0b436ed","tid":292963,"uid":35248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T05:01:31.000Z","msg":"自己同自己生自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e851a453bb3d903619a3015342b01aa1b90be8fb","tid":292963,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T13:43:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔太明樓主既意思,<br />\n點解當我係你某一世既轉世或者某階段時,<br />\n我會有可能自省, 或者會向善?<br />\n動機係咩? 理由係咩?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n當所有人都係自己，咁就冇分彼此 可以平等咁看待所有人<br />\n人其實最在意既都係自己 有時變得自我中心 唔識從別人出發 <br />\n死 我個腦開始亂 有冇人明我諗乜"},{"pid":"3bac84b682ac65655df0e3dadfcaa0600d1d831a","tid":292963,"uid":53947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T14:53:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔太明樓主既意思,<br />\n點解當我係你某一世既轉世或者某階段時,<br />\n我會有可能自省, 或者會向善?<br />\n動機係咩? 理由係咩?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n當所有人都係自己，咁就冇分彼此 可以平等咁看待所有人<br />\n人其實最在意既都係自己 有時變得自我中心 唔識從別人出發 <br />\n死 我個腦開始亂 有冇人明我諗乜</blockquote><br />\n明掛<br />\n可能秦始皇死咗投胎做一個現代人，佢死咗投胎做希特拉，希特拉投胎做你咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ec38f8602bf9c872e1d9a1afca91bad6902aa7a","tid":292963,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T15:40:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔太明樓主既意思,<br />\n點解當我係你某一世既轉世或者某階段時,<br />\n我會有可能自省, 或者會向善?<br />\n動機係咩? 理由係咩?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n當所有人都係自己，咁就冇分彼此 可以平等咁看待所有人<br />\n人其實最在意既都係自己 有時變得自我中心 唔識從別人出發 <br />\n死 我個腦開始亂 有冇人明我諗乜</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌我竟然睇得明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}